{"tid":2463414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國商務部長：全面策略反擊中國","createTime":"2021-03-26T16:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T16:42:07.000Z","uid":125168,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"116ede9a67fafbbad1ef0e41024f8168ef8483ba","tid":2463414,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"HK01<br />\n美國商務部長稱華府正制訂全面策略反擊中國<br />\n<br />\n美媒3月25日報道，美國商務部長雷蒙多（Gina Raimondo）接受全國公共廣播電台（NPR）節目訪問時說，美國新政府標誌中美關係的新篇章，而美國正制訂全面策略，包括如何保護美國工人、反擊中國等。<br />\n<br />\n全國公共廣播電台25日報道，雷蒙多接受節目《萬事皆曉》（All Things Considered）訪問時稱，拜登（Joe Biden）政府的開始標誌着中美關係出現新篇章。<br />\n<br />\n雷蒙多說，總統拜登目前專注於制定一項全面策略，包括如何保護美國工人、為美國公司營造公平競爭環境，及反擊中國。她說中國的行為正威脅美國的安全、繁榮及價值。<br />\n<br />\n雷蒙多稱，華府很清楚中國威脅之大，「我們已做好準備。」"},{"pid":"3a27ccc9e215eafa58020d90f537adc7814ed289","tid":2463414,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b754be6a776868623d931bc8b5f97a2bff666ce6","tid":2463414,"uid":283912,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"中美和好,反中撚炒哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3035a7b9eb507eee0be096d14779ac4f16f9dbe","tid":2463414,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b754be6a776868623d931bc8b5f97a2bff666ce6","tid":2463414,"uid":283912,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"中美和好,反中撚炒哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b17d6b0324f9cc341a7a8afa62a9c2721085c4b","tid":2463414,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"我好清楚我會發達，「已做好準備。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no